    "NER approaches Initially, researchers used traditional approaches, i.e., rule-based, dictionary-based, and knowledge-based.Currently, many studies use machine learning approaches, including deep learning.",
    "As the oldest approach, rulebased is now being abandoned because it has several disadvantages, such as depending on manual rules based on textual patterns [125,243]."
